attributes.review: I got this app in hopes of swaying my opinion on the tangerine with a bad toupee in office, but instead things didn’t go as planned. As soon as I got this app, I heard weird noises coming from my sister downstairs. I went to go check on her and I saw her eyes were rolled back into her head and she begun saying things like “Trump 2020” “Vote for the man who knows what he’s doing” “Screw Kanye West” so I knew things were not right. I shrugged it off thinking, maybe she just realized that he was amazing, but lo and behold, it started to affect my dreams. Every night I would have dreams of an orange with a long yellow feather on the top of it rolling up to me and saying “I’m making this country great, and this app even greater” I couldn’t move, speak, or even breathe. All I could do was watch as it smiled with it’s weird yellow teeth, and it’s large beady eyes staring back at me. I would wake up in cold sweats and on the floor, terrified of what may happen next. So of course I attempted to delete the app. As I did the secret service came into my house and attempted to get me to reinstall. Of course I did as they told me but stopped the download halfway through when they weren’t looking. Right now, I am currently hiding in my closet because I can hear the walking cheeto puff scream that he’s going to tear down my walls and make me pay for the repairs. I would strongly urge anyone to never download this app if they don’t want a run in with the sunburnt lemon and his secret service.
attributes.title: The Horrors of this App
